data.description:
Welcome to your future home nestled in the charming Falcon Ridge community! 

Built in 2015, this meticulously maintained property offers an array of modern upgrades for comfortable living. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, a spacious island, and an open layout perfect for entertaining. Upstairs, discover a versatile bonus loft and playful bedrooms featuring fun paint accents, adding a touch of personality to each space. With ample storage, a convenient mudroom from the 2-car garage, and a private backyard bordered by a serene tree-line, this home caters to practicality and relaxation. Enhanced with upgraded pest defense and water filtration systems ensures your peace of mind. Explore the community's amenities, including the pool and clubhouse, enhancing your lifestyle experience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this inviting space your own—schedule your showing today and embark on a journey to your dream home!
